NOTE  [[
    斯篇專作變數立名與賦值之驗證。
    考其立數、紀言、定陰陽之法，
    以驗編譯器轉譯之效。
]]


i have 1 num. called 1. name it [甲].                 NOTE [[ int 甲 = 1; ]]
i have 1 str. called [[噫吁戲]]. name it [唉呀].   NOTE [[ char* 唉呀 = "噫吁戲"; ]]
i have 1 bool. called false. name it [陰陽].               NOTE [[ bool 陰陽 = false; ]]
i have 1 any. called 1. name it [隨義].               NOTE [[ int 隨義 = 1]]

has a num 50. name it [大衍].                     NOTE [[ int 大衍 = 50; ]]
has a str [[問天地好在。]]. name it [文言].     NOTE [[ char* 文言 = "問天地好在。"; ]]

i have 1 num. called [甲]. print.
i have 1 str. called [唉呀]. print.
i have 1 bool. called [陰陽]. print.
i have 1 num. called [隨義]. print.
i have 1 num. called [大衍]. print.
i have 1 str. called [文言]. print.
